<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>HR Account Rejected</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      padding: 20px;
    "
  >
    <table
      align="center"
      width="600"
      style="
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      "
    >
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <h1 style="color: #d9534f;">‚ùå HR Account Rejected</h1>
          <p style="color: #555; font-size: 16px;">Hello, <b>{{user.full_name}}</b></p>
          <p style="color: #555; font-size: 16px;">
            We regret to inform you that your HR account request has been <b>rejected</b> by an administrator. 
            Unfortunately, you will not be able to access the HR system at this time.
          </p>
          <table
            width="100%"
            style="margin: 20px 0; border-collapse: collapse;"
          >
            <tr>
              <td
                style="
                  padding: 10px;
                  background-color: #f9f9f9;
                  border: 1px solid #ddd;
                "
              >
                <strong>Email:</strong> {{user.email}}
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td
                style="
                  padding: 10px;
                  background-color: #f9f9f9;
                  border: 1px solid #ddd;
                "
              >
                <strong>Phone Number:</strong> {{user.phone_number}}
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
          <p style="color: #555; font-size: 16px;">
            If you believe this was a mistake or have any questions, please contact our support team.
          </p>
          <p>
            <a
              href=""
              style="
                display: inline-block;
                padding: 12px 24px;
                font-size: 16px;
                font-weight: bold;
                color: #fff;
                background-color: #dc3545;
                text-decoration: none;
                border-radius: 5px;
                box-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
              "
            >
              Contact Support
            </a>
          </p>
          <p style="color: #777; font-size: 14px;">
            Thank you for your understanding.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
